item.description:
Error Control Operators  @ - Suppresses errors
extract()  It converts array keys into variable names and array values into variable value.
 // input array $state = array(&quot;AS&quot;=&gt;&quot;ASSAM&quot;, &quot;OR&quot;=&gt;&quot;ORRISA&quot;, &quot;KR&quot;=&gt;&quot;KERELA&quot;); extract($state); // after using extract() function echo&quot;\$AS is $AS\n\$KR is $KR\n\$OR is $OR&quot;; ------ $AS is ASSAM $KR is KERELA $OR is ORRISA
